      "speaker": ""
    },
    {
      "html": "<b>Mr. Wab </b><b><a name=\"_Toc40905774\">Kinew</a></b><b>�(Leader\nof the Official Opposition):</b> It's cheque day for seniors in Manitoba, with\neach letter sealed by a kiss from the Premier. However, we know that one thing\nthis Premier won't sign are the layoff notices that he's sending out across the\nprovince of Manitoba: 700 layoffs at Manitoba Hydro, thousands of people laid\noff from schools and many�<i>[interjection]</i> ",
