      "html": "<b>Mr. Wab </b><b><a name=\"_Toc40905777\">Kinew</a></b><b>�(Leader of the Official Opposition):</b> Well, it seems there's a bit\nof disagreement. We on this side of the House know that&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;these\ncuts will be very damaging, all the members on this side of the House.",
