      "html": "<b>Hon.\nBrian </b><b><a name=\"_Toc40905778\">Pallister</a></b><b>�(Premier):</b>\nI thank the member so much for raising the issue of transparency, Madam Speaker,\nin particular in the context of the Public Utilities Board. ",
