    {
      "html": "����� We know that the cuts, however, unfortunate as this may be, will go\nmuch further than Manitoba Hydro. We are already seeing the impact of the cuts\nat the universities and colleges on Manitoba, and we know it is the young\npeople, the students, the leaders of tomorrow, who will bear the brunt of these\ncuts.",
