    {
      "html": "<b>Hon.\nBrian </b><b><a name=\"_Toc40905781\">Pallister</a></b><b>�(Premier):</b> Well, let's do our best, Madam Speaker, to replace the\npandemic panic&nbsp;&nbsp;of the hyperbolic member and let's talk about&nbsp;&nbsp;our\nsupport programs for students. ",
