    { "html": "<b><i>Translation</i></b>", "index": "00379", "speaker": "" },
    {
      "html": "<i>The\nPremier of Manitoba (Mr. Pallister) has decided to put the PC campaign manager\nin charge of the provincial government. This is an unprecedented decision. It\nsends a clear message that the Premier wants to transform the Government of\nManitoba into a re-election machine for the Conservatives. This is corruption.�\n</i>�",
