      "speaker": ""
    },
    {
      "html": "<b>Mrs.\nSmith:</b> The Premier�sorry.",
      "index": "00657",
      "speaker": ""
    },
    {
      "html": "<b>Madam\nSpeaker:</b> I think the member's just realized what her error was. When\nreferring to members in the House, it is either by their positions or their\nconstituencies. ",
