      "html": "<b>Mr. Tom </b><b><a name=\"_Toc40905839\">Lindsey</a></b><b>�(Flin Flon):</b> I just want to put a couple of words on the record.\nI listened very carefully while the minister was speaking, and it seems that\nevery time one of the members of�opposite speaks, it's a different story. ",
