      "html": "����� The Premier said that while this has got to have these cuts because\nhe's going to redirect the money to health care. When that was proven multiple\ntimes to not be possible, now the minister comes up with a different story. And\nI just want to really reiterate what my colleague from Thompson said, that\nthis�these cuts can have devastating effects on the North. We've seen already,\na year or so ago, leaf�or Lynn Lake, the power was off. Their lone technician\nwas away�in South Indian Lake, I believe it was at the time�out of\ncommunication because, I'm sure you've heard me say, there's no cell phones in\nthe North, so it extended the period. ",
